WEBVTT

00:01.440 --> 00:05.196
All that is right is there,
all that is religion,

00:05.196 --> 00:09.920
and all that is Divine
is being challenged.

00:09.920 --> 00:14.076
No doubt about it.
I mean, I have no doubt.

00:14.076 --> 00:17.520
Now you know, when you got
your Realization,

00:17.520 --> 00:23.432
how difficult you found
even to meet people and talk to them

00:23.432 --> 00:30.880
really. How it was a problem
for you people to even face that.

00:30.880 --> 00:34.720
Because you used to get caught up,
and you felt it was too much,

00:34.720 --> 00:41.600
and all sorts of problems you had.
You understand that?

00:41.600 --> 00:52.080
Now, for Me, how difficult it is.

00:52.080 --> 00:55.680
For you, when you have only
little bit of Realization only,

00:55.680 --> 01:05.680
you started feeling.
For Me, how difficult it is?

01:05.680 --> 01:09.840
And the more it is difficult,
the more it is challenging you,

01:09.840 --> 01:16.400
the more I have to cleanse you,
the more my chakras start working.

01:16.400 --> 01:18.240
They start working very fast, you see.

01:18.240 --> 01:23.840
And you people are prepared as channels
to pass this light.

01:23.840 --> 01:26.560
And you know I've worked very hard
with you, done everything

01:26.560 --> 01:30.320
that is possible to help you.

01:30.320 --> 01:34.880
Now these channels must be kept
completely open to Me,

01:34.880 --> 01:39.280
and you must keep them also cleansed,
yourself, and you must receive

01:39.280 --> 01:43.360
the vibrations in a full way,
so that whatever I am trying to produce,

01:43.360 --> 01:44.960
you should be able to channelize it.

01:44.960 --> 01:48.800
Isn't it? You understand this?
You are all engineers and you understand.

01:48.800 --> 01:51.600
This is a big problem, you see,
for a source.

01:51.600 --> 01:56.000
Now what happens when your channels
are not clear, it comes back on Me.

01:56.000 --> 02:00.080
And in a way, it comes this way,
that the chakras are presided

02:00.080 --> 02:03.440
by the deities.
And the deities just get angry, you see.

02:03.440 --> 02:06.880
And I'll get sick, I can assure you,
I'll get sick with this.

02:06.880 --> 02:13.840
That's what I can see.
That's going to happen.

02:13.840 --> 02:16.800
So you must see the seriousness of it.

02:16.800 --> 02:22.880
It's not a casual thing, you see,
the way these people sometimes think.

02:22.880 --> 02:25.520
It's not about one person or another,
I'm saying.

02:25.520 --> 02:29.440
But I'm just telling you that
you will be held responsible.

02:29.440 --> 02:33.200
I really get sick in it.

02:33.200 --> 02:36.720
You see, we take it very casually,
in a very small way,

02:36.720 --> 02:39.040
while it is a very big force
which is flowing.

02:39.040 --> 02:42.320
It is a tremendous, dynamic force
which is flowing.

02:42.320 --> 02:47.680
And it will not harm you,
but it will only come back and harm Me.

02:47.680 --> 02:53.040
It happens, you know, I've seen
that I flow tremendous of flow.

02:53.040 --> 02:56.800
And it never forces you people,
it's just, it's destroyed out.

02:56.800 --> 03:00.080
It comes back and troubles Me.

03:00.080 --> 03:04.240
So the channel has to be opened out
and you have to work it out.

03:04.240 --> 03:09.200
I mean, what more can be done
that you should tell them?

03:09.200 --> 03:11.760
I'm willing to work it out
and cleanse you.

03:11.760 --> 03:13.520
But it happens like that.

03:13.520 --> 03:17.760
For example, last time in the Guru Puja,
the vibrations were too much,

03:17.760 --> 03:19.280
and you didn't receive some of it.

03:19.280 --> 03:24.240
But still, you have to take it up
really seriously.

03:24.240 --> 03:26.560
How many we are? Not too many.

03:26.560 --> 03:29.520
At the most, if you count,
sixty people at the most.

03:29.520 --> 03:33.360
But sixty people should do it fully,
in a full way.

03:33.360 --> 03:34.720
Then it will work out.

03:34.720 --> 03:37.440
I mean, you will not only have
your fulfilment,

03:37.440 --> 03:41.120
but it is the most important thing
to save this place.

03:41.120 --> 03:44.720
I mean, the whole Hell has to be
brought to this kingdom of heaven.

03:44.720 --> 03:47.120
How am I to do it?

03:47.120 --> 03:51.360
You are the channels. I'm not the channel.
This is one thing I tell you.

03:51.360 --> 03:53.200
And I'm desireless. I've no desire.

03:53.200 --> 03:57.200
If I get sick, I will get sick,
I tell you.

03:57.200 --> 04:02.640
I will have no objection about myself,
because I have no desire.

04:02.640 --> 04:05.600
You have to now ask that,
"I should be all right.

04:05.600 --> 04:07.680
There should be no more sickness in me."

04:07.680 --> 04:09.360
And that, "You should be able
to open out."

04:09.360 --> 04:11.040
It is you who have to pray to Me.

04:11.040 --> 04:12.560
Otherwise, I'm not going to do anything.

04:12.560 --> 04:15.200
I'm just going to accept sickness.

04:15.200 --> 04:17.160
This has happened at the time of Christ.

04:17.160 --> 04:23.280
It will happen again,
if you people don't follow.

04:23.280 --> 04:27.040
I'm not saying any individual,
but you all think about it.

04:27.040 --> 04:32.400
Now the trouble is, you see, it's very
easy to make a drama out of everything.

04:32.400 --> 04:36.560
Like Mr. Ronnie who comes to Me
and tortures my life morning till evening.

04:36.560 --> 04:39.920
His heart is broken somewhere, you know.

04:39.920 --> 04:45.040
And he has lost a woman's love
or some sort of a nonsense.

04:45.040 --> 04:48.400
I don't know from where I get
people like that.

04:48.400 --> 04:50.880
And every day he's torturing my life!

04:50.880 --> 04:55.040
But, today, I read a very interesting
article on this,

04:55.040 --> 04:58.704
that there's a psychologist -
I told you, in Times,

04:58.704 --> 05:00.316
it is in Times, or I tell it now.

05:00.316 --> 05:03.120
The psychologist, he says that,
"Those who suffer from this kind

05:03.120 --> 05:08.640
of love sickness should smell
rotten eggs."

05:08.640 --> 05:10.000
That's the solution.

05:10.000 --> 05:11.920
They should punish themselves
for doing that.

05:11.920 --> 05:14.480
And he has given ten punishments
for doing that.

05:14.480 --> 05:16.960
You must punish morning till evening
that you are suffering from this

05:16.960 --> 05:18.476
kind of a nonsense and that kind.

05:18.476 --> 05:22.560
And even if you remember such a person,
then you hit yourself with bullets,

05:22.560 --> 05:25.680
and cure yourself.
That's a very interesting article.

05:25.680 --> 05:29.040
He's a psychologist himself
and he suffered from a thing like that.

05:29.040 --> 05:33.360
But he said, "This, we can get rid of
with this kind of a treatment",

05:33.360 --> 05:38.960
which is a very sensible thing.

06:05.520 --> 06:58.160
Mother, this thing is on my mind
since month and month and month,

06:58.160 --> 06:59.680
that really what can we do?

06:59.680 --> 07:04.080
So you must have a, now in the ashram
especially, you must have a regular...

07:04.080 --> 07:05.680
Early in the morning you must get up.

07:05.680 --> 07:08.640
Those who have to stay in the ashram
must get up in the morning.

07:08.640 --> 07:11.360
Must do meditation, must go in
the evening meditation,

07:11.360 --> 07:13.040
and all nonsense should be given up.

07:13.040 --> 07:15.360
It is not a place just for people
to come and live there.

07:15.360 --> 07:18.480
That's one thing.
You must make it compulsory with them.

07:18.480 --> 07:20.960
Everybody must do meditation
and come down.

07:20.960 --> 07:22.800
Otherwise, what's the use of having
an ashram?

07:22.800 --> 07:28.400
It is like a boarding house,
a cheap boarding house, that's all.

07:28.400 --> 07:30.960
The ashram has been dispended now, Mother.

07:30.960 --> 07:31.360
Hum?

07:31.360 --> 07:33.640
There is, soon there is no ashram anymore.

07:33.640 --> 07:35.840
That's as far as I understand.

07:35.840 --> 07:43.360
Because everybody is going to move
some place, here and there.

07:43.360 --> 07:45.280
No, this mandate, it is not the point.

07:45.280 --> 07:46.640
We have to have a good place.

07:46.640 --> 07:50.320
We have to have a place where we have
to discipline people and tell them.

07:50.320 --> 07:54.000
But you all must decide within yourselves,
be genuine to yourself,

07:54.000 --> 07:55.840
what are we doing about it?

07:55.840 --> 07:58.000
You see, you come out
with your own problems,

07:58.000 --> 08:00.720
"I have got this problem.
I have got that problem."

08:00.720 --> 08:03.040
I mean, I am not here in a shop.

08:03.040 --> 08:06.000
It's all your problem.
You have to solve the problems

08:06.000 --> 08:16.400
of the whole world.
You understand, all of it?

08:16.400 --> 08:19.120
We have to have a place where
you have to be disciplined.

08:19.120 --> 08:20.800
You should decide among yourselves.

08:20.800 --> 08:22.640
You see, people like,
see like Vivekananda.

08:22.640 --> 08:24.480
Now you read his life.

08:24.480 --> 08:28.160
His Guru never gave him Realisation,
nothing of the kind.

08:28.160 --> 08:31.600
Just peace, about forty people
got to know.

08:31.600 --> 08:34.880
And you just see their lives,
how they dedicated themselves.

08:34.880 --> 08:39.200
Now Vivekananda was a man who had appeared
for ICS examination,

08:39.200 --> 08:42.000
Indian Civil Service,
in those days, it was the highest

08:42.000 --> 08:43.440
examination in India.

08:43.440 --> 08:49.520
And he resigned.
And how he dedicated himself!

08:49.520 --> 08:56.560
You must read his life
and you will be amazed.

08:56.560 --> 08:59.440
I mean, he decided that
he has to struggle.

08:59.440 --> 09:02.000
He never read about chakras or anything.

09:02.000 --> 09:06.800
And he went into it and he read it,
he studied it and took it up seriously.

09:06.800 --> 09:12.880
You see, it is a side issue
for all of you. How can you?

09:12.880 --> 09:17.440
It has to be the main thing.

09:17.440 --> 09:19.600
How much you are giving,
how much you are taking up,

09:19.600 --> 09:22.560
what responsibility?
You must be rushing forward to it.

09:22.560 --> 09:35.120
What responsibility we can take?
Think about it.

09:35.120 --> 09:38.320
I'm sorry I have to say this,
but you see, all kinds of these things

09:38.320 --> 09:44.240
are coming up and I feel that sort of,
I'll be left just high and dry

09:44.240 --> 09:47.600
in this country, as far as
the Western people are concerned.

09:47.600 --> 09:50.920
Crawley, I can say, I went there.
All my vibrations cleared out.

09:50.920 --> 09:54.160
Now they are saying that I have
to go to some other place,

09:54.160 --> 09:57.280
'Preston' or something. I'll go there.
It will clear out.

09:57.280 --> 10:02.240
Are we going to finish all the West
like this? Have we decided on that?

10:02.240 --> 10:06.160
I mean, it's a tremendous task
you must stay.

10:06.160 --> 10:13.200
Now the Indians cannot work
for the Western people.

10:13.200 --> 10:16.000
You should not forgive yourself
for doing anything wrong.

10:16.000 --> 10:19.440
You take yourself to task.
That's the way that he has said,

10:19.440 --> 10:22.720
that you smell a rotten egg.
Punish yourself for that, I don't mind.

10:22.720 --> 10:26.080
But also, if you do a good thing,
you give yourself a pinch.

10:26.080 --> 10:28.880
It's all right.
Don't punish to such an extent

10:28.880 --> 10:32.480
that you don't really mind also
what you do yourself.

10:32.480 --> 10:35.820
But it's not by bringing a flower
to Mataji and all that,

10:35.820 --> 10:37.920
nothing of the kind.
How many people have you realized so far?

10:37.920 --> 10:39.120
How many people you have talked to?

10:39.120 --> 10:44.859
And how far have you gone deep
into yourself?

10:44.859 --> 10:44.880
That's the big point.

10:44.880 --> 10:48.560
It's a very tremendous task,
I'm telling you.

10:48.560 --> 10:53.280
Never before, never before such vibrations
were given, nothing of the kind.

10:53.280 --> 10:57.200
Nobody knows all the secrets
that you know about reality.

10:57.200 --> 10:59.680
No one knows in the whole world.
I can tell you this.

10:59.680 --> 11:02.800
Even Markandeya may know
about my description and all that.

11:02.800 --> 11:05.840
But about vibrations and all these things,
he did not.

11:05.840 --> 11:09.040
It was not so much exposed even then.

11:09.040 --> 11:18.880
With all this knowledge, if this
is the condition, then what's this?

11:18.880 --> 11:22.320
That is what I want to give you
a question.

11:22.320 --> 11:25.680
I want to give you a question.
And I want you to think of it.

11:25.680 --> 11:30.880
All right? Understand, Christine?
You understand with a little gravity,

11:30.880 --> 11:35.600
all of you.
All the time crying and weeping

11:35.600 --> 11:43.520
or aggressing others is not the way.
What are you doing about it?

11:43.520 --> 11:46.480
Nobody is serious. You see,
just taking for this thing, you see,

11:46.480 --> 11:55.920
just... I can't understand.

11:55.920 --> 11:59.840
There is an Indian doctor who has come,
he got his Realisation,

11:59.840 --> 12:03.433
willing to invest 30 thousand pounds
here, he told Me.

12:03.433 --> 12:08.945
And he invests in a place
30 thousand pounds per month,

12:08.945 --> 12:10.960
it's all right.
So many things can be done.

12:10.960 --> 12:15.520
But what I'm saying is,
what about you people?

12:15.520 --> 12:20.713
Now we have to go to India next year, say,
you'll become a guru.

12:20.713 --> 12:27.760
I mean what a - they will know,
find you out in no time.

12:27.760 --> 12:29.480
Just think of it.

12:36.800 --> 12:40.160
It's a serious thing.

12:40.160 --> 12:43.280
So today, I just thought that after this
duty and all that,

12:43.280 --> 12:47.120
let us sit down, you take down
my vibrations, you finish them off.

12:47.120 --> 12:50.000
I have too much of it.
I will get sick, I think.

12:50.000 --> 12:55.280
I will get sick.
That's what I can see, clearly.

13:04.240 --> 13:08.800
So what can we have now?
Don't be upset about it,

13:08.800 --> 13:11.520
but you have to be serious
and good about it.

13:11.520 --> 13:14.560
You must know that it's
a very great thing.

13:14.560 --> 13:18.000
One has to bother about this thing.
This is very important.

13:18.000 --> 13:21.360
As my children, I'm talking to you
and I'm telling you that.

13:21.360 --> 13:25.000
Understand this possibility. Please.

13:25.000 --> 13:29.840
You must develop and come up to the point.

13:29.840 --> 13:32.080
It is no question of just improving you,

13:32.080 --> 13:33.600
like other gurus, you see, they will say,

13:33.600 --> 13:35.200
"I'll give you this
and I'll give you that."

13:35.200 --> 13:39.280
I'm not saying.
"I have given you already."

13:42.640 --> 13:44.560
No question of what I'm going to give you.

13:44.560 --> 13:48.800
It's a question what you are
going to give to others.

13:48.800 --> 13:52.720
You see, you must have more gravity
and understand that this is real Hell,

13:52.720 --> 14:02.400
real Hell where I've landed myself.
It's only because of you I've come.

14:02.400 --> 14:04.240
It's a very serious matter.

14:04.240 --> 14:07.280
You must give it a thought,
how far are you going to

14:07.280 --> 14:12.720
dedicate yourself.
It's just a subsidiary stuff for everyone.

14:12.720 --> 14:15.840
You see, for everyone,
it seems to be a subsidiary.

14:15.840 --> 14:18.080
Don't think that I'm saying about X or Y.

14:18.080 --> 14:20.000
If you think like that,
nothing can happen.

14:20.000 --> 14:28.800
You look at yourself and think,
"What am I doing about it?"

14:28.800 --> 14:32.720
You see, because, as you know,
Rustom himself said that day,

14:32.720 --> 14:36.800
"Mataji, you have no desire."
It's a fact. I have no desire.

14:36.800 --> 14:39.360
I have no desire even to live.

14:40.400 --> 14:44.240
I cannot desire to live,
nor can I desire to die.

14:44.240 --> 14:47.680
The 'desirelessness' is a state, you see.

14:47.680 --> 14:52.720
I have no desire.
But you must have desire.

14:52.720 --> 14:57.520
And first desire should be that,
"O Mother, let us be clean

14:57.520 --> 15:01.840
so that we pull all your vibrations
and we can give them."

15:01.840 --> 15:05.520
I was telling it to him, Rustom,
that, "You see, I am the source,

15:05.520 --> 15:09.920
all right? But the source has a problem.

15:09.920 --> 15:13.120
And the problem now I'm giving
to the channels that I've created.

15:14.000 --> 15:21.040
That the deities are preparing all that,
and when I demand it, they start.

15:21.040 --> 15:25.200
And suddenly what I find,
every channel is blocked.

15:25.200 --> 15:28.240
"This channel is blocked."
That's not because of your chakras.

15:28.240 --> 15:29.920
Chakras can be opened up.

15:29.920 --> 15:35.760
But because of your attitude,
attitude of callousness, I would say,

15:35.760 --> 15:39.600
of taking it for granted
and not taking it up seriously

15:39.600 --> 15:43.840
and with that gravity and understanding
as to what sort of a thing it is.

15:43.840 --> 15:52.720
Just think of it.
You have not valued yourself at all!

15:52.720 --> 15:56.400
I would not have given you all this
if you were not valuable people,

15:56.400 --> 16:00.160
if you were not strong people,
if you were not deep.

16:00.160 --> 16:04.160
I thought of you something,
I thought you to be real diamonds.

16:04.160 --> 16:09.760
That's why I have chiselled you.
But you must keep your facets clean.

16:09.760 --> 16:12.080
And you must keep your attitude clean.

16:12.080 --> 16:14.800
Otherwise, what will happen?
That all this will be rusted.

16:14.800 --> 16:22.480
And diamonds can also lose their lustre
if they fall into mud.

16:22.480 --> 16:25.440
And it is real Hell.
And this is what is happening now,

16:25.440 --> 16:29.760
that I have too much vibrations within Me
and I cannot pass it.

16:29.760 --> 16:34.640
And the deities are all angry, absolutely,
especially Christ.

16:34.640 --> 16:37.080
And that will happen,
I'll have to depart.

16:38.800 --> 16:42.880
No point to go on.
I'm just telling you that I'll get sick,

16:42.880 --> 16:53.680
I'll be very sick. You see that?

16:53.680 --> 16:57.356
You know, as soon as Christ died,
his Mother got sick.

16:57.356 --> 17:03.200
And She was sick throughout.
Because He was the one who was using

17:03.200 --> 17:05.680
her power.
Every time, you see, a Goddess has come

17:05.680 --> 17:10.560
or anything, she used her powers
to do some things in them.

17:10.560 --> 17:14.480
When she came as Durga, she spent it
in killing people and all that.

17:14.480 --> 17:17.760
Now here I am,
how can I kill my own children?

17:17.760 --> 17:22.560
The bhoots are in their heads only.
But you identify with them.

17:22.560 --> 17:36.080
The problem is you identify
and listen to them.

17:36.080 --> 17:38.960
One has to go all out.
Think about it.

17:38.960 --> 17:43.200
You have to go all out to do it.
It's a very serious thing.

17:43.200 --> 17:49.920
It's not something very, very casual
or anything. It's very easy.

17:49.920 --> 17:53.360
I can work out in the awareness
of people, but they cannot come

17:53.360 --> 18:04.480
near you people.
Too much of inertia, I think,

18:04.480 --> 18:15.120
too much of coming, too much.

18:15.120 --> 18:19.760
You may have to think about it
and think about your own valuation.

18:19.760 --> 18:28.400
Or else, I'll go back to India,
or get myself sick here,

18:28.400 --> 18:35.280
or currently, you get all right
and channelise the vibrations.

18:35.280 --> 18:39.360
To Me, it makes no difference
whether I die today or tomorrow,

18:39.360 --> 18:54.720
makes no difference.
But to you, it makes.
